title: Purchasing power change in the Netherlands 2015 to 2020
summary: In general Year on year percentage change has rose over the Year.
Year on year percentage change is roughly constant from 2015 to 2018, and lastly slightly increasing from 2018 to 2019.
The line rapidly increased by 160.0% from Year 2015 to 2016,remained stable by 88.46% from Year 2016 to 2017, and lastly, increased by 433.33% from Year 2018 to 2019.
The highest Year on year percentage change, of value 2.6 was reached at Year 2016
The lowest Year on year percentage change, of value 0.3 was reported at Year 2017, and 2018
